  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras/1374b80a35af9f7f1116aa6089088d75.avif?t=1767794941\" width=1560 height=662 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SILENCE IS YOUR ONLY ARMOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discreet</strong> is an asymmetric multiplayer experience where tension builds with every second. Whether you are the intruder or the defender, every decision leads to victory... or capture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras/a99dd6398ae1fb66a43caa6f233ee576.avif?t=1767794941\" width=1024 height=572 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR SIDE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Thieves:</strong> Work as a team to loot the house of its valuables. Hide in closets, dodge traps, and haul your loot back to the truck. One mistake, and you might be eliminated from the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Owner:</strong> Your home is your sanctuary. Set tactical traps to slow down thieves, patrol your halls, and search every corner. Your goal? Capture the intruders before they escape with your property.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras/02d538bc31846f45dae725c7e5341ee6.avif?t=1767794941\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras_big/02d538bc31846f45dae725c7e5341ee6.avif?t=1767794941 width=1560 height=870 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Asymmetric Gameplay:</strong> A high-stakes struggle between the thieves' discretion and the owner's vigilance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cat and Mouse :</strong> Closets are your only refuge, but stay alert: the owner can check them at any time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategy & Traps:</strong> As the owner, place your traps wisely to catch even the most agile thieves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race Against Time:</strong> The clock is ticking for the thieves. Be fast, be quiet, be efficient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras/55b9873df6360b069f92a53feccc5777.avif?t=1767794941\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras_big/55b9873df6360b069f92a53feccc5777.avif?t=1767794941 width=1560 height=870 /></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras/1374b80a35af9f7f1116aa6089088d75.avif?t=1767794941\" width=1560 height=662 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SILENCE IS YOUR ONLY ARMOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discreet</strong> is an asymmetric multiplayer experience where tension builds with every second. Whether you are the intruder or the defender, every decision leads to victory... or capture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras/a99dd6398ae1fb66a43caa6f233ee576.avif?t=1767794941\" width=1024 height=572 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR SIDE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Thieves:</strong> Work as a team to loot the house of its valuables. Hide in closets, dodge traps, and haul your loot back to the truck. One mistake, and you might be eliminated from the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Owner:</strong> Your home is your sanctuary. Set tactical traps to slow down thieves, patrol your halls, and search every corner. Your goal? Capture the intruders before they escape with your property.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras/02d538bc31846f45dae725c7e5341ee6.avif?t=1767794941\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras_big/02d538bc31846f45dae725c7e5341ee6.avif?t=1767794941 width=1560 height=870 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Asymmetric Gameplay:</strong> A high-stakes struggle between the thieves' discretion and the owner's vigilance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cat and Mouse :</strong> Closets are your only refuge, but stay alert: the owner can check them at any time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategy & Traps:</strong> As the owner, place your traps wisely to catch even the most agile thieves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race Against Time:</strong> The clock is ticking for the thieves. Be fast, be quiet, be efficient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras/55b9873df6360b069f92a53feccc5777.avif?t=1767794941\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280090/extras_big/55b9873df6360b069f92a53feccc5777.avif?t=1767794941 width=1560 height=870 /></span></p></li></ul>",
